      "content": "i hear u on the balance thing, but u said it kind of undermines the ability to protect people equally. doesn't that mean the secular state's version of \"equality\" is actually just everyone following the same set of rules regardless of their conscience? like, isn't it basically saying religious beliefs are less important than the state's rules?",
